<title>USA: WFS Financial sets 800,000-share buyback.</title>
<headline>WFS Financial sets 800,000-share buyback.</headline>
<dateline>IRVINE, Calif. 1997-04-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>WFS Financial Inc said Wednesday its board had approved the repuchase of up to 800,000 common shares.</p>
<p>Purchases will be made by the company's investment committee, it said.</p>
<p>((--New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610))</p>
